rows.label: bf06490150_0010
rows.name:
So it was hidden all the way out here...
No wonder we couldn't find it.

rows.label: bf06490150_0020
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]What-!

rows.label: bf06490150_0030
rows.name:
I'd just been wondering whether it was time to make an exit...
Thanks for saving me the trouble.

rows.label: bf06490150_0040
rows.name:
Lovely to see that tedious woman isn't
here to get in our way this time!

rows.label: bf06490150_0050
rows.name: Care to join me in a dance of death, Nia?

rows.label: bf06490150_0060
rows.name: I think I just threw up in my mouth a bit.

rows.label: bf06490150_0070
rows.name: Mean little girl.

rows.label: bf06490150_0080
rows.name: You've come for the Sanctus Chain, haven't you.

rows.label: bf06490150_0090
rows.name: Perceptive, kid.

rows.label: bf06490150_0100
rows.name:
Condescending much?
It's not like there's anything else here.

rows.label: bf06490150_0110
rows.name: You are SO mean.

rows.label: bf06490150_0120
rows.name: Now, hand it over nicely...

rows.label: bf06490150_0130
rows.name: ...would be the classic line, but no.

rows.label: bf06490150_0140
rows.name:
I'm not letting you escape with your lives.
For Shin's sake.

rows.label: bf06490150_0150
rows.name:
Where are Shin and Metsu, anyway?
There are a few things I need to ask them.

rows.label: bf06490150_0160
rows.name:
Frankly, I don't think they've got much interest
in what you have to say.

rows.label: bf06490150_0170
rows.name: Sure about that?

rows.label: bf06490150_0180
rows.name: Quite sure, yes.

rows.label: bf06490150_0190
rows.name: Not to interrupt the verbal sparring...

rows.label: bf06490150_0192
rows.name:
but how do you plan on doing anything
without your Blades?

rows.label: bf06490150_0200
rows.name: We're no pushovers, you know.

rows.label: bf06490150_0210
rows.name: Oh, we're quite aware of that.

rows.label: bf06490150_0215
rows.name: We just don't need them, you see.

rows.label: bf06490150_0220
rows.name: Explain yourself.

rows.label: bf06490150_0230
rows.name: Core Crystals?!

rows.label: bf06490150_0240
rows.name: They're Blades?!

rows.label: bf06490150_0250
rows.name: Worse- Flesh Eaters...

rows.label: bf06490150_0260
rows.name: Bravo! Very good!

rows.label: bf06490150_0270
rows.name: We've had many an interruption in the past...

rows.label: bf06490150_0280
rows.name:
but here, that seems less likely.
So let's go all out.

rows.label: bf06490150_0290
rows.name: You can try, but I assure you, we won't go down easy.

rows.label: bf06490150_0300
rows.name: I wouldn't have it any other way.

rows.label: bf06490150_0310
rows.name:
Like I said,
all out.
